bug.short_desc: Geany doesn't display underscore if zoom in text
bug.cf_doc_type: If docs needed, set a value

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1194219 geany bug underscore
Description of problem:
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): kernel-4.6.3-300.fc24.x86_64 geany-1.28-1.fc24.x86_64
How reproducible: always
Steps to Reproduce: 1. start geany 2. 4 times zoom in text in my case
Actual results: invisible underscore
Expected results: visible underscore
Additional info: See attachment geany_bug_underscore.png
I can reproduce it on EL7. It only happens on Zoom x 4 .. it does not happen with either zoom x3 or x5
